text: José Pardas (born 25 June 1955) is a Spanish rower. He competed in the men's coxless pair event at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Spain Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
